snippet.title: Eleven - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Eleven is a fan puzzle game to the great Netflix show Stranger Things.

The creator of this game owns NO right to the original material on which this fan game is based on. This game is also free and does NOT generate any revenue.

Desktop version of the game:
https://waldemar-umaniz.itch.io/eleven

Android version of the game:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.waldemar.umaniz.eleven
